    • initialize

      public void initialize(URL url, ResourceBundle resourceBundle)
      Populates the data fields with the current part data to be modified. Depending on part type, either sets Machine ID field (InHouse) or Company Name field (Outsourced).

    • OnActionSavePartMainMenu

      public void OnActionSavePartMainMenu(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent) throws IOException
      On click of Save button, saves the modified part to the Inventory and redirects user to main menu. Retrieves user input from the form to modify current part or create a new part object. Prevents invalid/empty data input and displays errors via dialog boxes.
      Parameters:
      actionEvent - the event that triggers the method
      Throws:
      IOException - exception
